emotional FREEDOM
memories are not real
they feel real, but really they are tangible
we remember them in the mind
and feel them in the body
memories are not permanent
we get used to the experiences that have shaped us
yet we can change and re program the past
we can regain control of our feelings
by changing our minds
Are you coping with stress, grief, anger, loneliness, fear, worry, shame, guilt and all kinds of emotions by going to food, work, chocolate, sugar, tobacco, drugs, alcohol, TV, FB?
what if you could have a relationship with these without the emotional attachments to them..that end up hurting you with weight gain,
crappy feelings, illness ect..when really we are looking for love..
but guess what, none of these love us..are our friends..
they can't hug us, kiss us..they might feel good in the moment
but usually feel bad after..
changing one belief at a time with faster EFT-Christina Law
a powerful technique that involves tapping on meridian points on the body. These points relate to organs that are imprinted with
emotional contents of life that don't just go away..they stay there till will intentionally let them go
book a session today.
You are in control, let me help you regain your power
now also offering tapping sessions via Skype
